Package: fmtr
Type: Package
Title: Contains functions for formatting data frames
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: David Bosak
Author@R: person("David", "Bosak", email = "dbosak01@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <dbosak01@gmail.com>
Description: Contains a set of functions that can be used to 
  format data frames.  The package aims to provide to R data frames 
  functionality similar to that of SASÂ® formats. Formats are assigned to
  the format attribute on data frame columns.  Then when the format() 
  function is called, a new data frame is created with the column data
  formatted as specified.  The fucntions also with with tidyverse tibbles.
